      <div id="aboutAuthor" class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/show/6937001.Yoshida_Kenk_">About Yoshida Kenkō</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class='bookAuthorProfile'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__topContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/6937001.Yoshida_Kenk_"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1389298429p3/6937001.jpg);'></div>
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__widgetContainer'>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__name'>
<a href="/author/show/6937001.Yoshida_Kenk_">Yoshida Kenkō
</a></div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__followerCount'>
50
followers
</div>

</div>
</div>
<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6506005612265154492"><b>Yoshida Kenkō</b> (吉田 兼好, 1283? – 1350?) was a Japanese author and Buddhist monk. His most famous work is <i>Tsurezuregusa</i> (<i>Essays in Idleness</i>), one of the most studied works of medieval Japanese literature. Kenko wrote during the Muromachi and Kamakura periods.</span>

</div>
</div>

<div class="clear"></div></div></div><div class="bigBoxBottom"></div></div>

  

    <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/author/list/6937001.Yoshida_Kenk_">Books by Yoshida Kenkō</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
